    "This phenomenon may be attributed to the fact that the longsequence capabilities of LLMs have not been specifically optimized for zero-shot recommendation tasks.",
    "If targeted optimizations were applied to enhance the ability of LLMs to handle task-specific prompts, it is reasonable to expect that improvements in performance could be achieved.",
